description: Broadway Hill is the complete restoration and addition of an 1870's brownstone overlooking Medal of Honor Park in South Boston. This significant offering combines a perfect blend of old and new, the epitome of Boston Proper. Situated directly across from Greenway, immerse yourself in one of Bostons' finest locales. Unit 2 is a second floor flat, featuring upgraded Bremtown cabinetry, along with custom coated brass hardware, and a Thermador appliance package. Open House June 22nd, 11:30am - 1pm.
